message.body: Hi! I guess we are partners again :) nice of you to help your brother out. Do you know what you're wearing to the wedding tomorrow?
Guess one of us we'll be getting the money :-)
Lol
Yes. I bought a dress and sandels. Everything is ready. Just have to iron the kids suits
Aww. Kids at weddings are the cutest! Have you won money before in these things? I never when lol :)
*win
No never. Its my first week
This wedding is really nice!
Aww thats good.
You said you were in it??
I love the linens :) no my hubby is a groomsman, his college roommate is the groom.
Is your wedding friends or family?
Family friend :-)
Did I say it right?? Lol. Or is it "friend of the family"??
Haha I think both work :) that's cool! They are playing gangam style and the mother of the groom is amazing!!!
Nice!!
Seems like a fun wedding
It was great! I'm still recovering :P is your wedding during the day or tonight?
Tonight. The bride walks in at 8
Ah that's a late wedding for Sunday :) what color is your dress? I never know what to wear to weddings...
Thats how our weddings always are. Could go up to 1am
Navy blue
Ah okay :) what community is that?
Arab :-)
Ah okay, I'm south Asian but the wedding I went to last night the bride and groom were Korean. I love Arabic music though! Will there be dancing?
Oh heck yes!! What's an Arab wedding without dancing lol. My sister in law loves Korean music
Hahaha awesome :) I lived in Egypt for a year during college so i think I'm stuck in 2003 as far as music goes but I like Nancy Ajram, Elissa, Rouby. I p
robably need to catch up on new music :)
Hhhh lol some good choices. I'm a fan of Elissa, and Nancy is still big too. She is one of the judges on "Arab Idol" (like American Idol). Ummm, Rouby ho
wever, was always a,waste of air lol
Hahahaha true but I'll never look at a stairmaster the same way again.
Hhhhhhhhh!!!!
Omg hilarious
